    "long_instructions": "Layer together the backing instruments in this track using loops and rests. Your song should include at least 4 different tracks that loop through the song but start and stop at different times\r\n\r\n<details>\r\n  <summary>Mini-rubric Details</summary>\r\n  <table>\r\n  <tr style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px\">\r\n\t  <td>Extensive Evidence</td>\r\n\t  <td>The song contains at least 4 different tracks that are looped and layered together to create a complex song. Multiple types of tracks are used with songs starting and stopping at differnet times.</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px\">\r\n\t  <td>Convincing Evidence</td>\r\n\t  <td>The song contains at least 4 different tracks that are layered together and start and stop at different times, but the song itself feels disjointed or jarring with how the sounds ebb and flow.</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px\">\r\n\t  <td>The song does not use at least 4 different tracks the majority of the tracks start and stop at the same time.</td>\r\n\t  <td>critera</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px\">\r\n\t  <td>No Evidence</td>\r\n\t  <td>The song does not use loops</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n</details>\r\n\r\n<details>\r\n  <summary>Validation Details</summary>\r\n  <table>\r\n  <tr style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px\">\r\n\t  <td>Condition</td>\r\n\t  <td>S/F?</td>\r\n\t  <td>Message</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px\">\r\n\t  <td>Song uses 1 loop or 0 loops</td>\r\n\t  <td>F</td>\r\n\t  <td> Make sure your song has multiple loops!</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr style=\"border: 1px solid black; padding: 1px\">\r\n\t  <td>Song does not use a rest block</td>\r\n\t  <td>F</td>\r\n\t  <td>Make sure your sounds are offset! You will need to use a rest block for this!</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n</details>",
